originalText.text: I’ve been going to Dr. Grace Su for over 10 years.   I had a terrible fear of going to the dentist.  It’s still there, but greatly diminished.  Dr. Su is comforting and patient. She gets to know you. She not only remembers me but things we discussed in the past.  I now have friends and family that see her.  She asks about my friends, mom and about work we are doing on our home.  She personalizes her relationships with her patients.  It’s like having a family member as your dentist.  Ohh - and she has Saturday hours.  You’re not missing work to see the dentist. Yay!
